### Actualizar tarea
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/ID_DE_TAREA
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Tarea actualizada",
  "completed": true
}

### Eliminar tarea
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/ID_DE_TAREA
Authorization: Bearer TU_TOKEN_AQUI